Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在國外有這樣的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說通過跟病人說話  使他們甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昏迷狀態下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以傳達到深層意識裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是否能理解話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話語？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是變得完全寫不出文章了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他有了位很好的擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香和要  你還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都來看望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  再一起去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加文化祭  運動會  還有從未參加過的社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我早就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初在保健室裡和我交談的是美歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我搭話的  的確是文歌沒錯  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美川文歌  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}小文自稱時用的是「私」（多用於女性自稱）\N美歌自稱時用的是「僕」（多用於年輕男生自稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  原來文伽也去了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是幫她製造一個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小文交上朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我喜歡上的  難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒那個心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見  工作熱心的文伽小姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的  有點棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我嗎  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死者寄來的這一點我明白  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要符合死後文的規定  什麼都可以送到喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  那就是傳說中的文伽的本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就奇怪你怎麼能長大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  是因為你並沒有死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苫  你沒說出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用文字傳達出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\bord0\fs29}沒\N說\N出\N去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  還沒告訴別的郵遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地來看我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  我哪有那麼閒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去玩吧  買木天蓼的錢還剩著些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是閒得很嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在看山  這次去看海吧  比如南方的小島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算緣分  你們也一塊來吧  現在放暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你很閒  我們接下來可要去工作  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還挺通情達理的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換  由我來決定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的是南方的小島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是國內的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不飛過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂旅行  是指連路途也要好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白  移動很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒錯咧  因為我會變成人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢是會應驗的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  千章也是郵遞員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交通事故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和對面行駛來的車  嘭地撞個正著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你開車技術超爛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笨啊  開車這種事是交給男人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於男人和女人的事  什麼都可以請教姊姊我喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是站在夕陽下  大喊了「我喜歡文歌」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎麼跟她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你住嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  這是你第一次住民宿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次…旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼  我們來指教你享受旅行的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔枕頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我也想扔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我來倒茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宮島？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那裡是無人島  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊的島？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌說目的地不是這  是旁邊的島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易和文歌再會了  不告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時只是嚇了一跳  並不是因為討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都那麼說了  你就再告白一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是初中時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都過了時效了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛是無所謂時效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是喜歡她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和夏香你無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為文歌是我的朋友  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把通訊功能用於偷聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊  你明明是當事人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告白了對吧  那個眼鏡男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的  或是有了其他喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人還是活人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自己吧  而且是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很明白  什麼是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你一直和父親相依為命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章有過很多次…戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是陳年往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  美川煌老師的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎  虧你能拿到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  我是預定了房間的白河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼陪我來南方的小島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那座島上有死後文的收信人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才問過阿姨  說那是無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文伽  有誰在那島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指郵遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  說不定只是具屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄屍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再講啦  這之後可是要去那個島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者很老實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  活著的人才比較可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是犯人在怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定剛殺掉  正把凶器埋進洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得很有趣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文歌  不要開這種奇怪的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  你要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶…器

Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  嚇到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是去掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鐮刀是用來除草的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真佩服  這麼年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都五年沒去掃墓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有個中意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對他告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知是沒有勇氣  或是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時電視上戀愛占卜說  戀愛的lucky chance是掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你也是單相思組員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外  大家都在單相思中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎   我對小文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難受吧  告白就像dead or alive吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上這條路  最後是生還是死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛或許可以成真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是失敗了  連朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  青春～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章沒有這種經歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  基本上屬於經常被人家告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個沒品的男生告白說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千章  我希望成為你的避雷之所」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概是想說「避雷針」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常應該說是「想成為守護你的盾」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也很沒品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章  你在倒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是未成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是未成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來了  戀愛的事不借點酒意怎麼說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那個眼鏡男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡什麼覺啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿身酒味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你喜歡的人吧  這可是旅行的樂趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼按順時針順序戀愛特訓  夏香第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關掉燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們一直鬧到早上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子們共處的晚上可是很寶貴的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學到不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了島上馬上去掃墓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的話  和我們一起游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  掃完墓以後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  是替誰掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爺爺  清澄的家原本在那島上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我爺爺的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我媽媽姓  所以姓氏不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺的  名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  你爺爺難道是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他結婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人沙灘～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  還是不知道文歌選這座島的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  能跟仗一起游泳的也就得是在無人島了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了我出生的鎮子  時隔多年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家  學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的商店  經常玩耍的公園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後都過了五十年了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變化的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母  朋友  大家都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過之後他也活了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的因為貓和他相遇的那人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點羨慕能長大的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這可不是食物喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也能來上墳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺  這兩位是文歌和千章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這的途中交上的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一生幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚  有了可愛的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後的願望也是  希望才藏能在我死後一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是清澄才藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人  會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺明明一直獨身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽是養女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候因為交通事故失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爺爺領養的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  千章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周的電影也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀美術館也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識千章你後  一直很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  從今以後  一直和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉我  再找一個不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  求婚的話  要有戒指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用墓碑代替
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子沒品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我宣誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
